  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to measure the quantities of food consumed at each meal by a
      representative part of the population of patients hospitalised in each department of the
      Champmaillot Geriatric Centre.

      To do so, the quantity eaten will be quantified by weighing the amounts served and
      subtracting the weight of the left-overs. These measurements will allow us to provide more
      appropriate meals in the second step.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
